Library bitlib
  Path:		src
  Modules:	Bitlib_prereq, Bitpath, Prefixset, Prefixmap
  CSources:	prereq.h, bitpath.h, bitpath_stubs.c
  CCOpt:	-I../src -Wall -g -O2
  DataFiles:
    prereq.h ($prefix/include/bitlib),
    bitpath.h ($prefix/include/bitlib)

Document bitlib
  Title:	Bitlib Reference
