  BuildTools+:	ocamldoc
  XOCamlbuildPath: src
  XOCamlbuildLibraries: bitlib
  DataFiles:	COPYING ($docdir), COPYING.LESSER ($docdir), README.mkd ($docdir)

Executable testsuite
